  "name": "RPlog_Fist_Full_of_Force_Users",
  "title": "A Fist Full of Force Users",
  "summary": "At the sprawling Imperial City spaceport on Coruscant, the Corellian Markus Lisardis waits with his offworld companion Simon Sezirok and the waifish Mira beside their ship the White Ghost, all three seeking the Jedi Luke Skywalker for their own reasons. Nearby, the swoop racer Enb'Zik strikes up an admiring conversation about a pair of Mantaray fighters with Jonathan Steiner before departing, while the Jedi General Tarroc D'agor, tinkering on his X-wing, senses the Force-sensitives and approaches to offer the trio his help. As Tarroc takes his leave, the blind young Jedi Ethan Katana arrives with his cybernetic Nek hound Bram, which bowls over Mira until she escapes into the ship. Wary of bounty hunters at first, Ethan questions the strangers and learns that Markus is plagued by intensifying nightmares and that Simon seeks the Jedi to aid his cursed companions. Recognizing them as people bound up in his own destiny, Ethan reveals he is Skywalker's student and invites them aboard his freighter to wait for the Master.",
